| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3902 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6c9c0ec8-3103-5a7f-bf1e-8a76beb90b96"
